The paper deals with network embedding, which is a subfield of machine learning and data mining. The use of neural networks and Bayesian personalized ranking also suggests a focus on supervised learning and recommendation systems, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.SI, cs.LG, and cs.AI.
